> @.13: Steve (?Coogle? - unclear)

> I know you typically don't interact with the box by asking questions, but
> have you ever tried telling them to communicate one at a time? It works for
> me most of the time when multiple voices crowd the box. Regardless, they
> definitely like communicating with you. I find the electronic voices and
> tones you get most interesting; they remind me of spiricom audio.
